headline: Booking Holdings Inc. to Present at the Nasdaq 51st Investor Conference
summary: Booking Holdings (NASDAQ: BKNG) today announced that Chief Financial Officer Ewout Steenbergen will speak at the Nasdaq 51st Investor Conference, held in association with Morgan Stanley at the May Fair Hotel in London, on December 11, beginning at 4:00 am ET / 9:00 am GMT. A live audio cast of the presentation will be available to the public at https://ir.bookingholdings.com/events. A replay will be available approximately 24 hours later and will remain available for 12 months.

headline: Agoda Highlights Five Urban Hikes for Adventurous Travelers
summary: Digital travel platform Agoda introduces five urban hikes across Asia, offering travelers a chance to experience the perfect blend of city life and nature. These hikes, ranging from family-friendly to more challenging trails, provide an unmatched perspective on some of Asia's most dynamic cities.
